DrillStateProperty.@Core.LongDescription:
Possible drill states are:
            <br>- `expanded` if a node has children which are included in the output set;
            <br>- `collapsed` if a node has [matching](#MatchCount) descendants but no children are included in the output set;
            <br>- `leaf` if a node has no [matching](#MatchCount) descendants and no children are included in the output set.
